title: Dos Hombre 20th Anniversary Special
itunes:title: Dos Hombre 20th Anniversary Special
description: This week on The Cigar Authority it's the 20th Anniversary celebration of Dos Hombre, and Dave Garofalo, Mr Jonathan and Chuck Morrison smoke them all to see which one's best! Which one will win? Only one way to find out! Sit back, light up, and enjoy the finer things in life with The Cigar Authority!
